Denmark Is Ready for Swift Military Action in Libya, Ritzau Says

-- B y   T a s n e e m   B r o g g e r
-- 
2011-03-18T07:01:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/denmark-is-ready-for-swift-military-action-in-libya-ritzau-says.html
  Denmark  is ready to provide “as
fast as possible a concrete contribution” to a United Nations-
backed air attack and a no-fly zone over  Libya , Ritzau reported,
citing Foreign Minister Lene Espersen.  A broad parliamentary majority supports the government’s
commitment to providing military assistance to any joint mission
to help insurgents in the North African country, the Copenhagen-
based newswire reported.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
